{"tid":588610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【立會補選】左報周街派溫提無身份證可以點投票 老董發功拉票","createTime":"2018-03-11T10:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T10:39:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6cd42bde469daf02f813b08e812f6544b61fad","tid":588610,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180311/57930791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180311%2F57930791&d=%2BRjYSswMQfuO7o%2FOD0kXxxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e0a57fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180311%2F57930791&h=f94c8768\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180311/57930791</a><br />\n<br />\n【立會補選】左報周街派溫提無身份證可以點投票 老董發功拉票<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞  2018-03-11 09:35:56 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n【新增動新聞】<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席董建華今早（11日）於香港公園體育館票站投票後，表示香港現正處於關鍵時刻，因此今次補選好重要。他又指，香港吵吵鬧鬧的時代應早日結束，港獨及自決將會為香港帶來很多危害，呼籲市民行使投票權，選出一個有建設性、做事實幹，並真心為香港服務的人進入立法會。<br />\n<br />\n另外，大公報今早於香港各區免費派發，於A1頭版大字寫出「建制派告急」，更詳細列出市民無身份證正本可以如何投票。報章指，如無身份證正本，可出示特區護照、或申請香港永久居民身份證收據、或簽證身份書、或海員證。它又清楚列出，若市民遺失又沒有替代文件，則須出示報失紙及身份證副本，及護照或旅遊證證正本。它又提醒市民不得只出示身份證副本、回鄉證或長者卡等進行投票。<br />\n<br />\n立法會補選分別於香港島、九龍西及新界東地方選區舉行，投票時間由早上7時30分開始，至晚上10時30分結束。具資格選民需帶備香港身分證正本，或指定的替代文件，到指定票站投票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立會補選新聞，《蘋果》一網睇晒<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/appledaily311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fappledaily311&d=%2BRjYSswMQfuO7o%2FOD0kXxxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ded07ca2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/appledaily311</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520732050_b617.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520732050_b617.png&h=a93cab47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（黃耀興攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520732124_b9e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520732124_b9e6.jpg&h=da31f38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（黃耀興攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520732127_d410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520732127_d410.jpg&h=9361c74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（黃耀興攝）(蘋果日報)"}]}